      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not really about charting a new course though. when you've seen the sights and the beauty and the grandness of it all, and you realize it doesn't actually change how empty you feel inside... it just feels like the tour is over. like the ticket has been used up. i dont think i want to see any more destinations. it just feels like i'm ready to just... check out of the trip.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
